These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, adventure, epic, western
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, snowmobile, train, airplane
1. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person driving the train##1
5. the person driving the airplane is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person driving the train##2
6. the person watching western movies is the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | western | zombie     | epic | adventure |
| Transport     | ship     | train | airplane  | snowmobile      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, country, r&b, pop
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, van, jet-ski, bike
1. the fan of country is on the left of the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of pop is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the van##1
5. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | country    | pop     | r&b  |
| Transport     | roller    | jet-ski | van | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, d&b, gospel, disco
4 different pets are kept: bird, mouse, goldfish, turtle
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
2. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the fan of disco##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b   | gospel   | techno  | disco |
| Pet           | mouse | turtle | goldfish | bird  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, sudoku, chess, photography
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, chinese, thai, indonesian
1. the indonesian is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's hobby is camping and the thai##2
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
4. the thai is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the italian is on the right of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | sudoku | camping | photography | chess  |
| Nationality   | chinese  | italian   | indonesian  | thai |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, sprite, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, fishing, baking, writing
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk    | cola   | sprite | tea    |
| Hobby      | fishing | skydiving | baking       | writing |

