.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, milk, 7up, cola
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, bike, van, car
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person driving the van is between the person driving the car and the person drinking 7up##2
3. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the van and the person drinking water##2
4. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | water | 7up | cola | milk |
| Transport   | bike | quad-bike  | van    | car  |

