.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, photography, reading, sudoku
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, sports, disaster, spy
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | sudoku | reading | writing | photography   |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | disaster | documentary      | spy |

