.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, hedgehog, turtle, goldfish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, ice-hockey, lacrosse, swimming
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is water-polo##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | mouse | hedgehog   | turtle      | goldfish      |
| Sport   | ice-hockey     | lacrosse | water-polo | swimming |

