3. the person driving the subway is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
5. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
6. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | reading | dancing | camping    | video-games      |
| Transport   | roller       | subway       | car | airplane |

