.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, spanish, malaysian, british
4 different pets are kept: lizard, ferret, pony, turtle
1. the spanish is on the far right##1
2. the japanese is the japanese##1
3. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
4. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the spanish##3
5. the malaysian is on the left or right of the british##3
6. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the british##3
7. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | japanese | malaysian  | british | spanish |
| Pet           | pony     | turtle | lizard    | ferret     |

