.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, pumpkin, onion, apricot
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, scientist, doctor, electrician
1. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the scientist##3
2. the scientist is on the right of the doctor##1
3. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
4. the scientist is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating onion is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | pumpkin  | grapes | apricot  | onion      |
| Job    | electrician | entrepreneur | doctor | scientist |

