The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, soul, electronic, gospel
1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
4. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
