.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-18::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, crime, thriller, mystery
4 different pets are kept: bird, rat, mouse, chinchilla
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person watching crime movies is the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the owner of the mouse is between the person watching mystery movies and the owner of the chinchilla##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | crime  | romance  | mystery |
| Pet           | bird    | chinchilla | mouse | rat |

