1. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the fisherman##1
2. the writer is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
3. the mechanic is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
4. the fisherman is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
5. the fisherman is on the left of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Food   | cauliflower        | grapefruit       | artichoke   | cranberry |
