.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, tea, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, golf, snowboarding, rugby
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
6. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea     | coffee     | tea          | almond-milk |
| Sport      | tennis | golf | rugby | snowboarding  |

 